<manpage>
    <sample url="sdk\operating_system\crt\libc\ctype\isalpha">isalpha</sample>
    <title>isalpha iswalpha</title>
    <volume>C 运行库函数</volume>
    <routine_idx> ctype_idx.htm </routine_idx>

    <description>
        <para>判断一个字符是否为字母（A C Z 或 a C z）。</para>
    </description>

    <syntax>
        <return_val>int</return_val>
        <func_name>isalpha</func_name>
        <parameters>
            <func_param>
                <param_type>int</param_type>
                <param_name>c</param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>需要判断的字符</para>
                </param_note>
            </func_param>
        </parameters>
    </syntax>


    <syntax>
        <return_val>int</return_val>
        <func_name>iswalpha</func_name>
        <parameters>
            <func_param>
                <param_type>int</param_type>
                <param_name>c</param_name>
                
            </func_param>
        </parameters>
    </syntax>
    <return>
        <para>如果c在A-Z或a-z的范围内,则isalpha返回一个非0值。iswalpha仅对于iswupper或iswlower为真的宽字符,(也就是,对于iswcntrl,iswdigit,iswpunct或iswspace都不为真的定义集之一的任何字符)返回非0值。如果c不满足这个测试条件则函数返回0。</para>
    </return>

    <requirements>
        <routine>
            <routine_name>isalpha</routine_name>
            <headerfile>ctype.h</headerfile>
            <compatibility>ANSI, Windows 2000, Elastos </compatibility>
        </routine>
        <routine>
            <routine_name>iswalpha</routine_name>
            <headerfile>ctype.h</headerfile>
            <compatibility>ANSI, Windows 2000, Elastos </compatibility>
        </routine>
    </requirements>

    <example>
<pre>
//==========================================================================
// Copyright (c) 2000-2008,  Elastos, Inc.  All Rights Reserved.
//==========================================================================

/* isalpha.cpp: This program uses isalpha to verify c
 * whether it is an alphabetic letter(A C Z or a C z).
 */

#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;
#include &lt;ctype.h&gt;

int main()
{
    int c = 67;
    if (isalpha(c)) {
        printf(&quot;the character is an alphabetic letter !\n&quot;);
    }
    else {
        printf(&quot;the character is not an alphabetic letter !\n&quot;);
    }

    return 0;
}
</pre>
    </example>
<result>
the character is an alphabetic letter !
</result>



